What is difference b/w PUT and Post.
Post - Create a new object on the server .
Put - it will update the value on server  which it already present.

What are commly used http methods .
Get -> Retrive object on the server .
Post ->Create object on the server
Put -> update the data on server which already exist .
delete -> Delete the data from server.

